cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use Entangled Alignment in your research, please cite the
  preprint below.
title: "Entangled Alignment: When Safety Is the Substrate"
abstract: >-
  A multi-agent system that reads a book chronologically and builds a
  knowledge graph of its concepts, relationships, and emergent themes
  via Gemini-powered agents coordinated through an MCP server. The
  paper argues that safety in AI systems must be the substrate rather
  than an overlay.
